episodes.overview: On this episode of Cribs, we head to Atlanta to mix it up in music producer Dallas Austin's luxurious living space. Then we're going a few rounds in Las Vegas with world champion boxer, Floyd Mayweather in his massive mansion. And finally we're kicking back with R & B sensation Lumidee in her New Jersey nest.

Then we're taking it to Texas to spend more quality time with Dallas Cowboy, Roy Williams in his remarkable residence. And finally we'll Walk It Out with rapper DJ Unk and his family in their Atlanta abode.

And finally, touch down in Cincinnati with NFL runningback Rudi Johnson as he gives you the grand tour of his sporty manor.

And finally, cozy up with Yellowcard front man, Ryan Key, and his precious pooch, Otis, in his Hollywood Hills home.

episodes.name: Taye Diggs / Martha Hunt / Nikki Garcia
episodes.overview: Broadway and on-screen actor Taye Diggs shows off his colorful Los Angeles home. Model Martha Hunt invites MTV inside her chic NYC apartment. Then, WWE Hall of Famer Nikki Garcia tours her Napa Valley vineyard and estate.

episodes.name: Vinny Guadagnino / Kaila Novak / Nick Viall
episodes.overview: MTV's Jersey Shore star Vinny debuts on CRIBS at his pristine Manhattan apartment. Soccer player and TikTok star Kai Novak shows off her fun candy filled Cali crib. Then, Bachelor star Nick Viall takes us around his cool, contemporary L.A. home.

episodes.name: Jonathan Bennett / Nicole Sullivan / DaniLeigh
episodes.overview: Actor Jonathan Bennett shows off his retro, Palm Springs oasis. Actor and comedian Nicole Sullivan takes us around her family's Los Angeles home. Then, R&B art

episodes.name: Alyssa Edwards / Atsuko Okatsuka / E.G Daily
episodes.overview: RuPauls Drag Race alum Alyssa Edwards shows off her blinged out abode in Mesquite, Texas. MTV stops by comedian Atsuko Okatsukas colorful L.A. house. Then, voice actor E.G. Daily from the Rugrats debuts her stunning home in the hills of Los Angeles

episodes.name: Mena Suvari / Anjali Bhimani / Shaun T
episodes.overview: MTV heads to the beach with actor Mena Suvari at her easy-breezy California bungalow. We cosplay with actor Anjali Bhimani at her marvelous Los Angeles crib. Then, celebrity fitness trainer Shaun T gives MTV a look inside his vibrant Arizona estate.

episodes.name: Jaren Jackson Jr. / Margaret Cho / Bobby Berk
episodes.overview: Professional basketball player Jaren Jackson Jr. tours his swanky Memphis mansion. Comedian Margaret Cho delights us at her unconventional Los Angeles sanctuary. Then, interior designer Bobby Berk shares an intimate look at his chic Palm Springs home.

episodes.name: Amanda Seales / Perez Hilton / Emelia Hartford
episodes.overview: Actor and comedian Amanda Seales wows us at her magical California chateau. Celeb news blogger Perez Hilton tours his familys Las Vegas house. Then, we cross the finish line with racecar driver and actor Emelia Hartfords cool Cali home.

episodes.name: Adrienne Bailon-Houghton & Israel Houghton / Vanessa Williams
episodes.overview: TV personality Adrienne Bailon and husband Israel Houghton takes us into their New York dream home. Then we cruise on over to the legendary Vanessa Williams lush estate.

episodes.name: Vivica A. Fox / Gus Kenworthy / C.J. Perry & Miro
episodes.overview: Actress Vivica A. Fox shows us her sultry home in Southern California. Then, we head to Olympic skier and American Horror Story actor Gus Kenworthys colorful crib. Then, we check out pro wrestler and Surreal Life alum CJ Perrys chic crib.

episodes.name: Jesse Metcalfe / Rumer Willis / Jenna Jameson
episodes.overview: We check out Jesse Metcalfes jaw-dropping California crash pad and then actor Rumer Willis invites MTV to her peaceful crib in Los Angeles. TV personality Jenna Jameson gives us a warm welcome into her home in Las Vegas.

episodes.name: Janel Parrish / Scotty Pippen Jr. / Dita Von Teese
episodes.overview: Pretty Little Liars actor Janel Parrish gives MTV an exclusive tour of her stylish modern home and basketball pro Scotty Pippen Jr. tours his sleek California condo. Then we enter the whimsical world of Dita Von Teese at her enchanting LA home.
